dd salt to taste as desired. Serve and enjoy!","url":"https://www.noracooks.com/vegan-cheese-grits/#wprm-recipe-9531-step-0-2"}],"aggregateRating":{"@type":"AggregateRating","ratingValue":"5","ratingCount":"4"},"recipeCategory":["Side Dish"],"recipeCuisine":["American"],"keywords":"cheese grits, grits recipe, vegan grits","nutrition":{"@type":"NutritionInformation","servingSize":"1 serving","calories":"163 kcal","carbohydrateContent":"23 g","proteinContent":"3 g","fatContent":"6 g","saturatedFatContent":"2 g","sodiumContent":"379 mg","fiberContent":"1 g","sugarContent":"1 g"},"@id":"https://www.noracooks.com/vegan-cheese-grits/#recipe","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://www.noracooks.com/vegan-cheese-grits/#article"},"mainEntityOfPage":"https://www.noracooks.com/vegan-cheese-grits/#webpage"}]}